These small droids are widespread. The term "utility droid" is used for many different models that varied widely in form and function. Some of them are at times referred as "astromech droids." 

Some models are used for advanced applied physics functions such as starship repair, astrogating, and even computer slicing and programming. Others perform more menial tasks such as janitorial duties and waste disposal.

Almost all are under one meter tall. They are equipped either with wheeled legs or small repulsorlift generators for movement, and painted the colours of their owner or simply left unadorned.

The uniform of a military Officer of the Sith Empire.

A noble of poise and posture. He looks to be in his late thirties, bits of grey creeping up his temples and into his hair, giving it a salt-and-pepper look. Regardless of his dashing appearance and charm, he is without a doubt a Sith Lord. A member of Revan's finest.

The Sith promote competition amongst their ranks, both among the Force Sensitives among their number and their rank and file troops. Those the most merciless, cruel and powerful amongst them are elevated, while those exhibiting softer tendencies are treated like fodder and find death sooner rather than later - often from friendly fire.

These are the former among them. Clad in finer armor and given access to the newest in Imperial weapons technology as reward for their faithful service to the Sith.
